ANS-hold diagnostic status
--------------------------
The DT-property variant reached BusyBox. An over-broad /proc/kmsg filter then
replayed historical PMGR output, so the module result did not drain before the
transport disconnected. The m1n1 proxy remained unresponsive after the
documented kisd restart and explicit DebugUSB re-entry. Live work stopped.

